## Overview

This pattern defines how experts work TOGETHER - not how they work individually (that's in `expert-workflow.md`).

**What this covers:**
- Cross-expert handoffs
- Group chat collaboration
- Multi-expert roundtables
- Expert recommendation (when to bring in other experts)
- Division of labor

**What this doesn't cover:**
- Individual workflow (see `expert-workflow.md`)
- Domain-specific work (see domain patterns: tech, content, strategy, legal)

